14/04/2009
TIRANA, Albania -- The main opposition Socialist Party (SP) presented its campaign platform Monday (April 13th), ahead of the parliamentary elections in June. SP leader Edi Rama said the SP prepared the programme with the help of European and US experts and intellectuals. It focuses on seven main areas, including education, rural development, environmental policies and domestic production. (Start, Shekulli, Telegrafi, VOA, Klan - 13/04/09) 
